<TEXT>
the massachusetts institute of 
technology is exporting americanstyle creativity to a japanese 
university eager to copy mits media laboratory where hardheaded 
science blends with imagination 
under the fiveyear 10 million agreement mit will help the 
japanese establish a lab with a loose creative atmosphere rare in 
japan 
theyre getting an experience with a style of research a way 
of running a research lab said nicholas negroponte the labs 
founder and director theyre creating a lab the style of which 
is similar to ours but the research content will be driven by 
those who run it 
