examining ways to use computers and interactive video games to help 
children learn 
the lab throws people of different disciplines together on the 
theory the mixture will produce applications with some value 
said cambridge media consultant larry levine you might get an 
engineer in with a political scientist and the likelihood is 
theyll produce something the engineer wouldnt have come up with 
alone 
