frequently during the campaign but was criticized for not doing 
enough to suppress antisemitism among some of his supporters 
the letter calls for dialogue leading to the elimination of 
mistrust bias and stereotypes to better knowledge of one 
another and an understanding based on respect for different 
religious traditions 
