i would not like either to simplify the situation or 
overdramatize it its most important not to fall into panic and 
especially hysterics and not to slip into accusations that will 
make us all feel ashamed tomorrow the situation that has emerged 
is really very serious it really is the culmination a certain 
so to speak situation has emerged here that in fact we ought to 
try and understand 
