of our congress as i see it in the real situation in which it 
proceeds when we all the entire society have reached the limit 
we must either confirm our choice or alter the course in essence 
the issue is such differences in tactical decisions in the rates 
of perestroika those after all are processes of real life a 
matter of search agreement i said then that we must defend this 
course despite all costs miscalculations errors that have 
resulted in difficult consequences and for which we must bear 
responsibility i am not evading responsibility but i can see 
responsibility above all in bringing this course to its logical 
conclusion so that it brings positive results for the entire 
