ambassador in france to discuss restoration of ties defending 
soviet human rights policies at a rights conference in 1977 and 
leading disarmament talks in 1985 on us and soviet intermediate 
and strategic nuclear weapons 
he later was brought back to moscow and made first deputy 
foreign minister solidifying his place in a new generation of 
flexible innovative diplomats 
