since the beginning of this academic year rushton has been 
forced to tape his 90minute lectures on theories of personality 
students enrolled in the course are obliged to pick up the tapes 
view them and telephone the professor with any questions 
rushton created an uproar last year by announcing that his 
research showed whites are more intelligent than blacks orientals 
are more intelligent than whites and the reasons are genetic and 
evolutionary 
university officials said last fall that forcing rushton to tape 
