died in 1953 it occupied a spot on central square until it was 
moved in 1968 and its place taken by skanderbeg albanias 
15thcentury national hero 
a statue of vladimir i lenin founder of the soviet state 
still stands across from the vacant plinth where stalin stood 
in tiranas socalled student city the ramshackle room that now 
