reminiscent of the makeshift operations that bred revolution across 
eastern europe last year 
but the new democrats here face a much tougher struggle to 
overturn communist rule 
those who buzz around the new democratic party of albanias 
dilapidated headquarters seem undaunted 
a primitive duplicating machine clanks out copies of the partys 
