prostitutes for parties at a beach house near san diego they said 
dixon crafted a scheme to divert loan advances to pay rent on the 
house and doctored records to hide vernons ownership of the house 
from thrift regulators 
the house at solana beach calif was a hotel and office for 
vernon as it expanded into the southern california real estate 
market dixon testified he said that in hindsight hiring women to 
attend the parties was inappropriate but not illegal 
