yettoemerge highdefinition television industry 
by controlling both the manufacture of the hardware and the 
making of the movies the japanese would be able to dictate which 
format is adopted in the united states for highdefinition 
television and eventually to dominate that market he argued 
these guys are looking at the future 20 years down the 
road he said 
but matsushitas lawyers said govideo had failed to prove that 
a temporary restraining order was warranted they argued that there 
has to be a showing of immediate irreparable damage 
